{
  "stem": "3605.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I choose that name so close to my original name because I had a diploma from the sewing school on my name, Jadzia Strykowska.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was so much alike that one [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] letter could have been just an omission.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was hoping on Aryan paper maybe that it's going to give me a-- a possibility to do something and be-- help with something or earn something.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was like another identification, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was to support my papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I smuggled into the ghetto and gave my-- to the Piotrkow ghetto-- and gave my father those [NON-ENGLISH] papers, which is the junk-collectors' papers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had a great reunion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We-- it was almost close to a year when I didn't see him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was extremely, extremely fond of my parents, especially somehow of my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was his little girl when I was still 17, you would think.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And at that time, in 1942, I was approaching 17.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was close before the High Holidays.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And since we haven't seen each other, and since we didn't [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] know [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] whether we will ever see each other again, he kind of insisted that I should wait with him over the High Holidays.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I kind of felt this wasn't so much to ask.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I alone wanted it, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we spent-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] We spent very special holidays together, like-- realizing that this might be it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The last time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Everything kind of was like the last experience.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The Rosh Hashanah and the Yom Kippur, I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[SOBS] And my father was attached there to a rabbi, too, that he prayed in a special shtiebel.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
